room_title: Escape room "Pharaoh’s Curse" by Escape Medina in Akron
room_description: You and your team of explorers stumble across the discovery of a lifetime, a mummies tomb. To the legend it’s known as Pharaoh’s curse! Someone in your group triggers an ancient hidden trap intended to entrap potential tomb raiders forever. With only 60 minutes of oxygen left, will you find your way out or become part of pharaohs curse and trapped forever!
